c:[["$","section",null,{"className":"pt-12 pb-16 px-5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#27ae60] to-[#2ecc71] text-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-4xl mb-4 block","children":"🔵"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4","children":"穩定燃燒型"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto","children":"你的代謝引擎運轉得不錯，繼續保持。"}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#2a2520] border-l-4 pl-5 font-semibold mb-8","style":{"borderLeftColor":"#27ae60"},"children":"你大概是那種會注意飲食、偶爾會運動、睡眠還算正常的人。不過別太得意——代謝是動態的，壓力、睡眠、飲食習慣的改變都可能讓你滑到其他類型。繼續保持就是最好的策略。"}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"pb-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-12","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"🧠"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"你的身體正在好好運轉"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"恭喜你，在這個高壓、外食、久坐的時代，能維持代謝穩定真的是了不起的事。\n\n你的胰島素敏感度正常、壓力荷爾蒙還在合理範圍、睡眠和飲食的節律沒有被嚴重打亂。這些不是理所當然的——而是你每天的小習慣累積起來的結果。"}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"⚠️"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"不過，代謝是動態的"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"代謝不是一個固定的狀態，它會隨著你的生活方式而變化。一次連續出差、一段高壓期、一個月的睡眠不足，都可能讓你從穩定燃燒滑到其他類型。\n\n所以不需要做更多，只需要繼續做你正在做的事：好好吃、好好睡、偶爾動一動。保持就是最好的進步。"}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"💝"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"但你身邊的人可能需要幫助"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"你的朋友、同事、家人，可能正在經歷上面某一種代謝困擾。他們可能覺得是自己意志力不夠、不夠努力、或是身體壞掉了。\n\n你可以把這份測驗傳給他們。也許你已經知道的事，正好是他們需要聽到的——「不是你的錯，是方法不對。」"}]]}]]}]}],null,["$","section",null,{"className":"py-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-6","children":["💡 給","穩定燃燒","的你"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","div","0",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#27ae60"},"children":1}],"你現在的狀態不錯，但代謝是動態的。繼續保持就是最好的策略。"]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#27ae60"},"children":2}],"你可能覺得自己沒什麼特別的——但能夠好好吃飯、好好睡覺、好好過生活，在現在這個時代就是一種了不起的能力。"]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#27ae60"},"children":3}],"把這個測驗傳給你身邊那個正在跟體重苦戰的朋友。也許他需要的不是更多意志力，而是知道「不是他的錯」。"]}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 px-5 bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-xl mx-auto text-center","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[#6b6560] mb-2","children":"你不用一個人搞懂這些"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"tex